headline.main: PRINCE OLAF IS HERE; PRAISES WAR EFFORT; Spirit of People of Norway to Win Unshaken, He Says

lead_paragraph: Crown Prince Olaf of Norway, arriving yesterday at La Guardia Field aboard a transatlantic clipper, emphasized that despite the "growing tyranny of oppression and the strengthening of terror in Norway, the spirit of the people is unchanged in its determination to win through."
